edu.harvard.integer.service.yaml

Interface YamlManagerInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseManagerInterface
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    YamlManagerLocalInterface, YamlManagerRemoteInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    YamlManager

    public interface YamlManagerInterface
extends BaseManagerInterface
    The YamlManager is used to import a YAML file. The current YAML file types supported are Technology Tree, VendorContianment and VendorIdentifier
